title: It was cold and windy. How Keric volunteers conquered Veľký Rozsutec
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Volunteers Suna Uzun from Turkey and Sebastian Pellizzari from Austria talk about one of their first hikes in Slovakia. Did they find any gold at the top of Veľký Rozsutec in the national park Malá Fatra? 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
